ccacb5369ee56062202","tid":1487494,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"hkie 同 istructe 無左 mutual recognition, 估唔到仲有人考 istructe...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"咁HKIE/RPE擺番係英國又係咪一張廢紙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"我假設樓主係香港打工......."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"咁HKIE/RPE係英國/英聯邦國家係咪完全冇用？"},{"pid":"597e5cf1789a39f0bc8d9f9c524ae01416b361de","tid":1487494,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c693f50c18fe751f0d7fc48467be2b78e44aa808","tid":1487494,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b04078c00481581bd4c3fb6825facc11cfb040","tid":1487494,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab52185de1928866ed5e18e5a2889899631841e","tid":1487494,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"咁HKIE/RPE擺番係英國又係咪一張廢紙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"我假設樓主係香港打工......."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"咁HKIE/RPE係英國/英聯邦國家係咪完全冇用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:10:03.000Z","msg":"英：無話一定要mistructe/mice至可以執業/簽名。building我唔熟，但係civil structures就睇clients要design cert or check cert要乜人簽。好多時只要求appropriate/recognized 學會會員就簽得。我有啲印度，歐盟國民同事只有自己祖家嘅牌。<br />\n<br />\n澳/紐：我唔會hkie係當地認唔認。只係十年前英國經濟唔好，身邊有同事移民去澳洲。我查過mice/mistructe係當地被認可(大約即係移民局搵澳洲會評估外人個資格是否同澳洲資格相同之類)。mhkie(str)有無用我真係唔知。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大：就算有mistructe都好似得一個省免考筆個part。加拿大，美國，台灣考牌制度相似，同hkie/istructe/ice考試方法好唔同。我諗mhkie係楓葉國無乜用。<br />\n<br />\n其他英聯邦國家，好似印度，南非&hellip;&hellip;俾錢我都唔去。無查過mhkie/mistructe有無用。不過我有啲有mistructe朋友，後contractor請去做design manager之類&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"d494e9a94cf4e829b4248cb696ff47da88035480","tid":1487494,"uid":170013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1ae6b9bd86669c78cc22a53931236b3b18a488","tid":1487494,"uid":73270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"大家好！小弟想開個Group ，一齊大家交流資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 互相照應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要入請留tg <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"有興趣啊，可以留個tg俾我嗎🙏🏼"}]}